item.title: Poker Mastery - Get The Mental Edge in Your Poker Game
item.description: Poker Mastery - Get The Mental Edge in Your Poker Game 5 Star Reviews Great course learnt a lot and would highly recommend Alan Kirwan’s course Robert Glass The course is relaxing and easy to follow Patrick Good course for me. Ning Yu Hypnosis for Poker inner game mastery Guided Hypnosis was created to help you achieve your goals by simulating a private hypnosis session with me. This hypnosis course will help you Learn why everyone knows Poker is not just a game of skill and a sprinkling of good luck but a mental game and a game of self control.
